<p class="text-justify">
    Oh look, we received a postcard from a little boy called Juan.
    He is not convinced that Santa is real.
    That is why he encrypted his christmas wish to hide it from his parents.
    Only Santa could encrypt his letter and give him the correct present.
    Let's figure out his wish to convince him of Santas existence.
    He also attached some instructions to his letter:
</p>
